### GraphQL - Get All Receivables
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { getAllReceivables(size: 10) { total receivables { id id_recebivel codigo_cliente valor_original data_vencimento } } }"
}

### GraphQL - Get Customer Balance
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { getCustomerBalance(codigo_cliente: \"123456\", data_inicio: \"2025-01-01\", data_fim: \"2026-12-31\") { codigo_cliente periodo { inicio fim } total_recebiveis saldo_total saldo_formatado } }"
}

