### GraphQL - Combined Query Example
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { indexCount: getIndexCount { count } topCustomer: getTopCustomer { codigo_cliente total_recebiveis } recentReceivables: getAllReceivables(size: 5) { total receivables { id_recebivel codigo_cliente valor_original } } }"
}

### GraphQL - Formatted Query with Variables
POST http://localhost:8080/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetReceivablesByCustomerAndDueDate($codigo_cliente: String!, $data_inicio: String!, $data_fim: String!, $from: Int, $size: Int) { getReceivablesByCustomerAndDueDate(codigo_cliente: $codigo_cliente, data_inicio: $data_inicio, data_fim: $data_fim, from: $from, size: $size) { total receivables { id_recebivel codigo_cliente valor_original data_vencimento } } }",
  "variables": {
    "codigo_cliente": "CLI-10001",
    "data_inicio": "2025-01-01",
    "data_fim": "2026-12-31",
    "from": 0,
    "size": 20
  }
}
